Package: ggtree
Type: Package
Title: visualizing phylogenetic tree and heterogenous associated data based on
    grammar of graphics
Version: 0.99.2
Author: Guangchuang Yu
Maintainer: Guangchuang Yu <guangchuangyu@gmail.com>
Description: ggtree extends the ggplot2 plotting system which implemented the
    grammar of graphics. ggtree is designed for visualizing phylogenetic tree
    and associated annotation data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    ggplot2
Imports:
    ape,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    methods
Suggests:
    gridExtra,
    phylobase,
    BiocStyle,
    knitr,
    testthat,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: https://github.com/GuangchuangYu/ggtree
